&gt; &gt; I am not saying this about any single level of researcher but all 
&gt; of 
&gt; &gt; us myself included have fallen into this rut. We are not learning 
&gt; &gt; anything, All our efforts are amounting to nothing.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; We already know that we are communicating with someone or 
&gt; something. 
&gt; &gt; I believe we have all come to believe that through our personal 
&gt; &gt; research and the evidence presented by all of us.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Within the last year the technology and potential of this type of 
&gt; &gt; research has exceeded all expectations in it&#39;s quality and speed 
&gt; of 
&gt; &gt; development. We are actually letting it go to waste.
