&gt; &gt; side of the line has had a hand in some of us developing this new 
&gt; &gt; equipment and methods of research be it obvious or subtle.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; But our methods of research have not excelled, we are conducting 
&gt; &gt; research in the same manner as we did when there where only about 
&gt; 5 
&gt; &gt; of us in the whole world actively doing this research.
